Rule 8     entries -> entry
Rule 9     entries -> entries COMMA entry
Rule 10    entry -> LABEL
Rule 11    entry -> NUMBER LABEL
Rule 12    entry -> DICE LABEL

Terminals, with rules where they appear

COMMA                : 9
DICE                 : 3 12
LABEL                : 3 10 11 12
NUMBER               : 6 11
RANGE                : 7
SEPARATOR            : 3 6 7
error                : 

